"{\"uid\": \"velo.outsideonline.com-olympics-usa-cycling-announces-2024-olympic-road-cycling-team\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Powered byOutside  OYAMA, JAPAN - JULY 24: Richard Carapaz of Team Ecuador &amp; Brandon McNulty of Team United States in the breakaway during the Men's road race at the Fuji International Speedway on day one of the Tokyo 2020 Olympic Games on July 24, 2021 in Oyama, Shizuoka, Japan.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 81, \"end\": 96, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brandon McNulty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9915281967702503, \"rank\": 0.0046951236711893045, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shizuoka_Prefecture\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.508913555044478e-16, \"text\": \"Shizuoka\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shizuoka_Prefecture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shizuoka_Prefecture\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9969569236558621, \"rank\": 0.0018007259762763542, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by Tim de Waele/Getty Images)(Photo: Tim de Waele/Getty Images)  USA Cycling has announced the five athletes who will be racing the road race and and time trial at theParis Olympic Gamesnext month.Chlo\\u00e9 Dygertand Taylor Knibb will take on both the women's road race and time trial.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999017826009124, \"rank\": 6.94061004189842e-05, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.578913371338235e-28, \"text\": \"USA Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Cycling\"}, {\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylor Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the men's side, Brandon McNulty and Magnus Sheffield will participate in both events, while Matteo Jorgenson will compete in the road race.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brandon McNulty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\"}, {\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magnus_Sheffield\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Magnus Sheffield\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magnus_Sheffield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magnus_Sheffield\"}, {\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matteo_Jorgenson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matteo Jorgenson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matteo_Jorgenson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matteo_Jorgenson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dygert (Canyon-Sram) earned her place on the team after winning the 2023 UCI Time Trial World Championships.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\", \"score\": 0.9294047605330832, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canyon-Sram\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\"}, {\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\", \"score\": 0.9999999687343011, \"rank\": 3.1265763203076166e-08, \"text\": \"Time Trial\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She comes in with Olympic experience already, having won a silver medal on the track in 2016 in Team Pursuit, and a bronze medal in the same event in the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7214247384332937e-21, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will be competing in Team Pursuit again this summer.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7214247384332937e-21, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's truly a blessing,\\\" Dygert said.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am truly blessed to be selected for my third Olympic Games in USA colors.\\\"\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9872238143925135, \"rank\": 0.010398327389750044, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be Dygert's second time competing in the Olympic road race and time trial.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She finished 31st in the road race and 7th in the time trial in Tokyo, after returning from a career threatening injury less than a year before.\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9976853234352036, \"rank\": 0.002319927210194092, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taylor Knibbis also an experienced Olympian, but in triathlon, not cycling.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She won a silver medal in the mixed relay triathlon event in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9976853234352036, \"rank\": 0.002319927210194092, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She earned her spot on the 2024 Olympic road race team last monthby winning the US time trial national championship racein Charleston, West Virginia, besting some of the nation's top road racers who compete in the top ranks of cycling.\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US time\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charleston,_West_Virginia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charleston, West Virginia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charleston,_West_Virginia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charleston,_West_Virginia\"}, {\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.7673579620945182, \"rank\": 0.21847194076842466, \"text\": \"Virginia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_men's_basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the time trial is familiar to Knibb, the road racing will be more of a challenge, one that she's fully aware of.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.569246929837633e-13, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Cycling has a very steep learning curve, and I am\\u00a0simultaneously excited and nervous for what lies ahead,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 2020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to the road race and time trial, Knibb will also be competing in triathlon again, making her a rare two-sport athlete.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2067, \"end\": 2072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.569246929837633e-13, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very honored, grateful, and excited for the opportunity to represent Team USA with USA Cycling.\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would not have been possible without the support of my amazing family, friends, coaches, manager, sponsors, and USA Triathlon.\\\"\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2371, \"end\": 2384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Triathlon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.547377408845465e-12, \"text\": \"USA Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Triathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brandon McNulty(UAE Team Emirates) earned his spot on Team USA after winning the US time trial national championship last month by nearly a minute.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2388, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brandon McNulty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McNulty\"}, {\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UAE_Team_Emirates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UAE Team Emirates\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UAE_Team_Emirates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UAE_Team_Emirates\"}, {\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.973657854010835, \"rank\": 0.0269398748776482, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2469, \"end\": 2476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US time\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will compete in both the time trial and road race.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McNulty had a memorable Olympic debut in Tokyo, lasting to the end of an attritional road race and attacking with eventual gold medal winner Richard Carapaz with 25km to go.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\", \"score\": 0.9999999994838618, \"rank\": 5.163450987662157e-10, \"text\": \"McNulty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\"}, {\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9976853234352036, \"rank\": 0.002319927210194092, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2732, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Carapaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Richard Carapaz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Carapaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Carapaz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McNulty could not hold on after Carapaz surged again with 6km to go, but came home for an impressive sixth place.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2765, \"end\": 2772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\", \"score\": 0.9999999994838618, \"rank\": 5.163450987662157e-10, \"text\": \"McNulty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\"}, {\"begin\": 2797, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Carapaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carapaz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Carapaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Carapaz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That top result - sixth in the road race - just\\u00a0 motivates me all the more,\\\" McNulty said.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2958, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\", \"score\": 0.9999999994838618, \"rank\": 5.163450987662157e-10, \"text\": \"McNulty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_McNulty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The race was super aggressive, I relive it all the time.\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 3029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At home in Arizona and Girona, I am already training with 100 percent focus on Paris.\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3041, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Wildcats\", \"score\": 0.9999999883411875, \"rank\": 8.372111803389253e-09, \"text\": \"Arizona\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Wildcats\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_Wildcats\"}, {\"begin\": 3053, \"end\": 3059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girona_FC\", \"score\": 0.9997789015528841, \"rank\": 0.00022114610189279355, \"text\": \"Girona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girona_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girona_FC\"}, {\"begin\": 3109, \"end\": 3114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996821316, \"rank\": 3.180946272377337e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My goal?\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bring back a medal!\\\"\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The other two spots in the men's road events are taken up by Olympic debutants in Magnus Sheffield and Matteo Jorgenson.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3229, \"end\": 3245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magnus_Sheffield\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Magnus Sheffield\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magnus_Sheffield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magnus_Sheffield\"}, {\"begin\": 3250, \"end\": 3266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matteo_Jorgenson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matteo Jorgenson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matteo_Jorgenson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matteo_Jorgenson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sheffield(Ineos Grenadiers) has been having a strong year in the time trial, podiuming several times in individual time trial stages, including last month at the Giro d'Italia on stage 7.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3269, \"end\": 3278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"score\": 0.6391834727885681, \"rank\": 0.5633433005317933, \"text\": \"Sheffield\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\"}, {\"begin\": 3279, \"end\": 3295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos Grenadiers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has also put up some impressive road race results, including sixth at the Tour of Flanders.\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels like a dream come true,\\\" said Sheffield.\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3593, \"end\": 3602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"score\": 0.6391834727885681, \"rank\": 0.5633433005317933, \"text\": \"Sheffield\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Going to the Olympics was one of my biggest goals growing up.\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am\\u00a0 incredibly proud to represent the U.S. in Paris as well as all the people that have helped me along\\u00a0 the way.\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3715, \"end\": 3720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996821316, \"rank\": 3.180946272377337e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think it will fully sink in until I am there.\\\"\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jorgenson(Visma-Lease a bike) is in the midst of a major breakthrough season, having won Paris-Nice earlier in the season and Dwars door Vlaanderen during the spring classics campaign, showing he's a threat in stage races and one-day events like the Olympics alike.\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 4105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jorgenson will be competing in just the road race.\", \"from\": 4106, \"to\": 4156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics were always a part of my childhood,\\\" Jorgenson said.\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember spending entire summers watching sports I had never heard of and admiring the athletes.\", \"from\": 4225, \"to\": 4324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For sure it had a big effect on me and was one of the reasons I decided to pursue a career as a pro athlete.\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being able to race in Paris, especially following the best year of my career, is a dream come true.\\\"\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4456, \"end\": 4461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996821316, \"rank\": 3.180946272377337e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}]}"